Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:03:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,with the infinite\Nself and realizing that one is all that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is forever.\NIn the first lecture, we said that in
