Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.24,0:46:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,perceptions,\Nways of seeing things, ways of
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.83,0:46:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,interpreting them.\NConditionalities that we've been
