Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.92,0:46:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to God?\NWould I rather be right or would I
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.28,0:46:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,rather realize the presence of God?\NSo willingness then always puts up
