Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.20,0:48:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm afraid if it disappears,\Nyou become invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.52,0:48:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeps you here to some degree. You need\None want and one attachment. Something
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.64,0:48:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was showing people a picture of it\Nyesterday. Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.40,0:48:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to renounce it. Am I\Nwilling to renounce it? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.76,0:48:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it just went. Well, okay. Okay.\NUh,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.28,0:49:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,all right. So, what we're developing is\Nthe spiritual muscles
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.40,0:49:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so that when you need them,\Nthey're there. As I step over the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.48,0:49:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,rattlesnake,\Nthere I am on the top of Schnebly Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.20,0:49:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking at a big place there.\NAnd as I step over it, good God
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.24,0:49:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,almighty, there is the hugest rattler\Nyou ever saw. Good lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.64,0:49:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,H. And in that instant there was letting\Ngo at absolute death depth and absolute
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.55,0:49:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,letting goess. All fear disappeared. All\Nall perception of it as a possible enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.28,0:49:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,or it and in his place there was a\Nprofound stillness and peace that was
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.04,0:49:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,infinitely powerful.\NThe presence of love of presence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.92,0:49:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is\Nso powerful it sweeps away everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.64,0:50:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the snake is held there\Nsuspended. It's like that can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.07,0:50:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That profound state of peace, the\Nstillness of the presence of God holds
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.24,0:50:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,all within itself\Nand nothing can withstand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.11,0:50:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you need it, when you need it,\Nthat capacity was already perfected to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.31,0:50:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,completely let go totally at all at\Ngreat depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.55,0:50:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And otherwise I wouldn't be here today\Ncuz a snake would have just done a snake
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.68,0:50:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,thing and I just do my human thing and\Nyou know
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.00,0:50:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we both would have been in trouble you\Nknow
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.20,0:50:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so a higher state prevailed h so you\Nnever know when you're going to need
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.92,0:50:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,this capacity\Nyou have to be and and one meditative uh
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.68,0:50:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,con style is to look at all the things\Nuh in your life and keep surrendering
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.83,0:50:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,what what there is about it. Aversion or\Nattachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.31,0:51:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the willingness to surrender\Nattachments and aversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.68,0:51:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I really care if the rattlesnake\Nkills me? To tell you the truth, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.72,0:51:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Why not now? I mean later it's\Ncertain. So why not now? But the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.31,0:51:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,difference of the body any day. uh\Nwhether it's today or tomorrow doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.80,0:51:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,really make any difference\Nthat capacity then to surrender to let
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.35,0:51:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,go\Nis a is a form of love. See we call love
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.72,0:51:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,a calibrated level of consciousness but\Nactually all these things from here up
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.04,0:51:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,are all forms of love. This is love in\Nthe in the form of the capacity to tell
