Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.31,0:52:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because if you really accept who you\Nare, nothing can make you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.52,0:52:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,uncomfortable. Nothing can be uh,\Nyou know, injurious to your self-esteem
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.83,0:52:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,because if you're quite evolved, you\Ndon't have any self-esteem.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.31,0:52:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How can injure people injure your\Nself-esteem when you don't have any?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.00,0:52:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I said if what do you need self-esteem\Nfor?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.44,0:52:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Does a bird need self-esteem to fly? It\Ndoesn't need this self-esteem. I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.44,0:52:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,this is an pertinance that you pass\Naround to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.52,0:52:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's always somebody in the news 6:30\Nwho's
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.68,0:52:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,whose sensitivities have been offended.\NI mean, you can't live in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.44,0:52:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,without offending somebody's sensitivity\Nnowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.80,0:52:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You get up and give the lady a se her\Nseat. You feel that she feels offended
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.16,0:52:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're insulting her that\Nfeminine is weaker than male or
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.83,0:52:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,something. If you hold the door, if you\Ndon't hold the door, so I mean you're
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.20,0:53:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,offending somebody no matter what you\Ndo. You see nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.28,0:53:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So every night somebody's offended by\Nsomething.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.35,0:53:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it this week? This week there\Nwas a group in Berkeley that might be
