Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.28,0:53:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to celebrate 9/11. There was a group\Nthat politically felt people might be
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.04,0:53:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,offended by showing the red, white, and\Nblue on the campus. So, you can be
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.24,0:53:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,offended by the flag. You can be\Noffended by anything. And lots of people
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.07,0:53:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,are offended by God or any mention\Nthereof.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.80,0:53:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. They have a political\Ngroup, don't they? I forget all about
