Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.44,0:54:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and\Nall right. So try to pretend um
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.59,0:54:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,when you totally accept the reality of\Nwho you are, you can't be offended.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.88,0:54:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fat. So they can call you any\Nname they want to. Shorty, four eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.16,0:54:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,dumbbell, right?\NSomebody calls you a liar. Tell them I'm
