Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.64,0:54:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,all these problems in life is cuz I'm so\Nstupid and I'm so ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.52,0:55:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.\NIt's cuz I'm stupid. Well, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.24,0:55:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, once you accept the possible\Ndownside of everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.88,0:55:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,uh, nobody can offend you.\NYou're greedy. Yeah, I am greedy. I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.52,0:55:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Green, man. Give me what I want. You\Nknow what I mean? You just become that
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.76,0:55:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,which people say you are. You're\Nimpervious. There's nothing you can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.40,0:55:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.\NSo, you see, we can't make neuroticism
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.20,0:55:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the law of the land. You're not going to\Nbe able to not offend somebody. See,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.88,0:55:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because some people are going to be\Noffended if you do, and some people are
