Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.28,0:56:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,context then h\Nso truth then what we call truth which
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.40,0:56:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is usually discontent\Ndepends on context. What's truth today
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.35,0:56:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is not truth tomorrow.\NWhat's appropriate today is not
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.68,0:56:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,appropriate tomorrow. What's appropriate\Nin this circumstance is not appropriate
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.04,0:56:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in that circumstance. You see what I'm\Nsaying?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.72,0:56:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficulty then with one\Nirrationality is it doesn't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.59,0:56:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that meaning\Ncomes out of context not just content.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.76,0:56:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So the political position that is\Ncausing most the aggravations in society
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.76,0:56:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,right now is the inability to discern\Nthat context totally changes content.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.44,0:56:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's suitable in peace is not the same\Nas suitable in war. what's suitable
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.40,0:56:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,uh in the inner city streets is not\Nsuitable in Park Avenue and site. So
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.59,0:57:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,what is appropriate shifts depending on\Ncontext who when the totality of the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.79,0:57:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,universe. So context is really the\Ntotality of the whole history of the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.44,0:57:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,entire universe. And if people are going\Nto insist on looking for a cause, you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.11,0:57:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,tell the cause of it is the totality of\Nthe entire universe throughout all of
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.44,0:57:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,time. And that's why this little piece\Nof dust is sitting right where it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.55,0:57:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, and trying to pin it on me,\Nman. Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.96,0:57:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the universe's fault.\NI'll be some lawyer, wouldn't I? I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.16,0:57:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,love to be a lawyer. I'd love to be a\Nlawyer, man. I just
