Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.07,1:00:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we can start from the top top down. out\Nof compassion for yourself. Then you're
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.88,1:01:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,willing to let go of that which brings\Nyou pain, suffering, guilt,
