Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.52,1:01:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,out of love for oneself, out of\Ncompassion for oneself,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.16,1:01:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,out of compassion for myself,\NI'm not going to allow myself to fall
