Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.88,1:02:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,everything then our willingness to let\Nthings go. We do it all the time as a
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.79,1:02:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,style of life.\NOne expression of love then is devotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.92,1:02:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And in spiritual work that devotion\Nbecomes more and more intense. It
