Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.11,1:02:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,my favorite sneakers and uh it seems\Ntrivial." Oh no. The capacity let go of
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.92,1:02:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,your favorite sneakers and not grieve\Nabout them or be angry at somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.44,1:02:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,stealing them or something.\Ncapacity to surrender your sneakers is
