Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.68,1:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The willing to let go of anything and\Neverything to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.07,1:06:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, you're asked to let go all\Nof it, even physicality.
